{"tid":2115574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（企硬）印度要求中国撤軍　「沒有談判餘地」","createTime":"2020-07-19T14:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T15:35:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c736988942998ed3ea39978d70aa910a38d3d455","tid":2115574,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:58:44.000Z","msg":"印度媒體上周六（18日）報道，在中印第四輪軍長級會談中，印方傳達了一個明確信息，即中國軍隊必須撤出地區，且沒有談判餘地。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士稱，雙方長達15個小時的會談是友好的，但印方傳達的信息很明確，即要求中國軍隊撤軍，除非恢復5月5日之前的現狀，否則甚麼都無法實現。報道指，印方不會迴避使用武力，實際上已經做了充分的準備。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200719/bkn-20200719181858420-0719_00952_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"96826ae032d32926139f25b849f200ec682c3119","tid":2115574,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f14d66b5e6310bccd8618d4b48198553fa12a79a","tid":2115574,"uid":231583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79f329a9ed9728bffd9a3220ab1baa6d13a8bfee","tid":2115574,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"幾時公佈之前啲傷亡數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4d667c27be77ebf0e86d22f5fa7126a3aed3a3","tid":2115574,"uid":54721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"乜都唔駛講<br />\n直接打左先<br />\n佢就會收皮"},{"pid":"878640a39d280c005642935e789cf1a8e0e6e17d","tid":2115574,"uid":43428,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"暴力可以解決問題 <br />\n暴力最可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26e63a2bb491636e19cac39823e8416cdd7855c","tid":2115574,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a4d667c27be77ebf0e86d22f5fa7126a3aed3a3","tid":2115574,"uid":54721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T1